67379.「<pc>さま……。\n 災厄の王の 魔力により\n その地は 常に深い闇に覆わ:
<pc>... the land has always been
shrouded in deep darkness by the magical power
of the King of Calamity.

67380.「私たち 世告げの姫のチカラで\n その地を覆う 闇を払いましょう。:
Let us, the Oracle Princesses, use our power
to dispel the darkness that covers the land.

67382.「<cs_pchero>さま……。\n 災厄の王は 目覚めてはいますが\n 深い:
<cs_pchero>... the King of Calamity is
awake, but seems to be in a deep slumber...

67383.「この世界が 実体を保っていられる時間は\n 災厄の王が目覚めるまでの ３０分ほ:
The only time this world can remain an entity is the half hour or so before the King of Calamity awakens... a time we must not let
slip away.

67385.「さすがは 時の王者 <cs_pchero>さま。\n みごとな戦いでした。:
As expected of the champion of time
<cs_pchero>. It was a splendid battle.

67386.「これで……アストルティアは 破滅から\n 救われました。この記念すべき日は 永:
With this, Astoltia was saved from
destruction. This momentous day will forever
be etched in the memory of the people.

67387.「我々 世告げの姫は\n 災厄の王が倒されたという報せを\n これから 各国の王:
We, the Oracle Princess, will now go to the
kings of the world with the news that the King
of Calamity has been defeated.

67388.「<cs_pchero>さま。\n あなたこそ 真の王者と呼ぶにふさわしい……。:
<cs_pchero>. You are what I would call a
true champion and I thank you from the bottom
of my heart.

67391.「妙ですね……。\n 災厄の王が 倒されたというのに\n まがまがしい邪気は 辺:
Strange... the King of Calamity has been
vanquished, and yet a haunting evil spirit
lingers in the air...

67392.「なぜ 今まで 気がつかなかったのか……。\n 災厄の王が鎮座する場所としては\:
I don't know why I didn't notice it before,
but for a place where the King of Calamity
resides, this place is far too quiet...

67393.「災厄の王……まがまがしい邪気……。\n そして この神殿の静けさ……。:
The King of Calamity... the blinding evil...
and the serenity of this temple...

67394.「ああ……。なんということでしょう。\n これは まさか……！？: Oh... what a surprise. This is no way...!

67395.「始まりは…… これからだというのか……。:
The beginning... you say, is just the
beginning...

67396.「おお……。なぜ ここまで試練を与える……。\n これ以上 何を試すというのだ…:
Oh... why do you put us through so many
trials... and what more do you want to try...
when we are so powerless? What more can...

67397.「これまで 私たちの やってきたことは\n すべて 無駄な あがきだったというの:
All we have done so far has been a futile
attempt!

67399.「……すみません。心配を かけましたね。: I'm sorry. I'm sorry for worrying you.

67400.「<cs_pchero>さま。お話ししたいことが……。\n のちほど 落陽の草原:
<cs_pchero>. I would like to talk to you...
please come to Cosette's place in Sunset
Meadow later.

72784.「今こそ 時の王者のチカラで\n 災厄の王を 討つのです！:
Now, use the power of the Champion of Time to
strike down the King of Calamity!
